## ğŸ”§ Installation
For now (local development):
```bash
git clone <this-repo>
cd aima_toolkit
python -m pip install -e .
```

Then in Python:
```python
from aima_toolkit.SearchProblemPackage.SearchAlgorithms.InformedSearch.a_star_search import astar
```

